"title": "5229: bed",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5229: bed",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A household item of furniture set aside for sleep, rest and quietness.</p>\n<h2>Various kinds of bed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:11\">DEU 3:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:4\">AMO 6:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:34\">ACT 9:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:6\">MAT 9:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:11-Mark2:12\">MRK 2:11–2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:18-Luke5:19\">LUK 5:18–5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:4\">MRK 2:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:24\">LUK 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:15\">ACT 5:15</a></p>\n<h2>The bed as a place of rest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:2\">1SA 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:5\">2SA 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:7\">2SA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:13\">2SA 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:8\">EST 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:15\">JOB 33:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:8\">PSA 139:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:16-Prov7:17\">PRO 7:16–7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:14\">PRO 26:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:20\">ISA 28:20</a> <em>Beds were not always comfortable</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:5\">DAN 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:1\">DAN 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:7\">LUK 11:7</a></p>\n<h2>The bed as a place of recuperation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:3\">PSA 41:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:8\">ACT 28:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:2\">GEN 48:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:18\">EXO 21:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:5\">2SA 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:19\">1KI 17:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:4\">2KI 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:21\">2KI 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:13-Job7:14\">JOB 7:13–7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:19\">JOB 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:27\">DAN 8:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:14\">MAT 8:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:30\">MRK 1:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:22\">REV 2:22</a></p>\n<h2>The bed as a place in which to be alone</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:4\">PSA 4:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1\">MIC 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:4\">1KI 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:12\">2KI 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:2\">2KI 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:6\">PSA 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:6\">PSA 63:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:20\">ECC 10:20</a></p>\n<h2>The bed representing sexual union</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:30\">DEU 22:30</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:7\">GEN 39:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:20\">DEU 27:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:11\">2SA 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:1\">1CH 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:10\">EZK 22:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:17\">EZK 23:17</a></p>\n<h2>Unusual places used as beds</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:11\">GEN 28:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:5\">1KI 19:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:5\">JON 1:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:38\">MRK 4:38</a></p>\n<h2>Bed associated with a description of apostasy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:7\">ISA 57:7</a></strong></p>",
